snippet.textDisplay:
Letter to Coke Studio to release the new Song!



Hey there, Melodious Maestros of Coke Studio,

I've got a bone to pick with you! I'm writing to you with a mix of anticipation and a tiny, good-natured grudge.

Could you, would you, in a boat? Could you, would you, with a goat? Release the New song, I mean. The Initial songs were a musical appetizer that's got me craving the main course, and I'm here, plate in hand, ready for the feast.

In all seriousness, your music is the soundtrack to my life, and I can't wait to hit the replay button on the new song. So, pretty please, with a cherry on top, let us know when we can expect the new track.

Rock on and keep the hits coming!

Yours in tune,
Awaam
